{"tid":531001,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Creed 2選中反派演員Drago之子 今年11月上映","createTime":"2018-01-16T10:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T15:54:21.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8c12a3fcf10b7e3daa698508a91e5a41e423baf3","tid":531001,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T10:52:45.000Z","msg":"拳擊片《奎迪》續集選中反派演員：羅馬尼亞拳擊手、外號「Big Nasty」的Florian Munteanu將在《奎迪2》飾演蘇聯拳王德拉戈的兒子，身高193、體重110公斤的Munteanu，想必出拳也很有力。<br />\n<br />\n《洛奇4》中飾德拉戈的杜夫&middot;龍格爾也會回歸，當年正是德拉戈打死了老拳王阿波羅，也就是《奎迪》主角阿多尼斯的爸爸，兩代人的恩怨這次誓要解決。<br />\n<br />\n《奎迪》主演邁克爾&middot;B&middot;喬丹、史泰龍也會回歸續集，年輕的拳手阿多尼斯繼續朝冠軍進發，但導演瑞恩&middot;庫格勒不會回來，這部導演已定為《滑板少年》的Steven Caple Jr.，2018年11月21日北美上映，時間相當緊了~<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/185220_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F185220_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=d484f104&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/185227_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F185227_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=05ca630c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d83db4069fa5acbdf06beff9ace2b4edc4810bc5","tid":531001,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:50:14.000Z","msg":"屌你仲有第二集 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身諗住當係 rocky 7 完結 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1dace50a24c3753f78aa1404e718e214f2ca0a","tid":531001,"uid":61443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:50:50.000Z","msg":"creed 個 一 shot 落係精彩既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d1acd7f9ea5ff8c3a799d6ef23decf278ce949","tid":531001,"uid":4260,"like